#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This module allows configuring activities. Activities are a way to have "
"multiple &plasma; setups, with each a different set of widgets and themes. "
"Some activities can be private. Such activities do not track your actions. "
"For example, they do not track what recent document you opened."
msgstr ""
"Ta modul omogoča konfiguriranje dejavnosti. Dejavnosti so način, kako imeti "
"več &plasma; nastavitev, pri čemer ima vsaka drugačen nabor gradnikov in "
"tem. Nekatere dejavnosti so lahko zasebne. Takšne dejavnosti ne sledijo "
"vašim dejanjem. Na primer ne spremljajo, kateri dokument ste nedavno odprli."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The module is divided into two tabs: <link linkend=\"activities-main"
"\"><guilabel>Activities</guilabel></link> and <link linkend=\"activities-"
"switching\"><guilabel>Switching</guilabel></link>."
msgstr ""
"Modul je razdeljen na dva zavihka: <link linkend=\"activities-main"
"\"><guilabel>Dejavnosti</guilabel></link> in <link linkend=\"activities-"
"switching\"><guilabel>Spreminjanje</guilabel></link>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Activities</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Dejavnosti</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This tab lists your current activities. Hover items in the list with the "
"mouse pointer to reveal the buttons to configure or remove activities."
msgstr ""
"V tem zavihku so navedene vaše trenutne dejavnosti. Z miškinim kazalcem "
"podrsajte elemente na seznamu, da se prikažejo gumbi za konfiguriranje ali "
"odstranitev dejavnosti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"configure.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> overlay button to "
"configure activity. You can change the following activity parameters:"
msgstr ""
"Uporabite <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"configure.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> prekrivni gumb za "
"konfiguriranje dejavnosti. Spremenite lahko naslednje parametre dejavnosti:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Icon"
msgstr "Ikona"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The icon of activity can be seen on the activity manager selector of the "
"&plasma; panel. Click on the current icon to choose some system-wide icon or "
"browse the file system to select a custom icon."
msgstr ""
"Ikona dejavnosti je vidna v izbirniku upravitelja dejavnosti na pultu "
"&plasma;. Kliknite na trenutno ikono, če želite izbrati ikono za celoten "
"sistem, ali pa pobrskajte po datotečnem sistemu in izberite ikono po meri."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "Name"
msgstr "Ime"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "Give your activity a recognizable name."
msgstr "Dajte svoji dejavnosti prepoznavno ime."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Opis"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A free-form description of the activity that is shown below the name on the "
"activity manager selector of the &plasma; panel."
msgstr ""
"Opis dejavnosti v poljubni obliki, ki je prikazan pod imenom v izbirniku "
"upravitelja dejavnosti na plošči &plasma;."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "Privacy"
msgstr "Zasebnost"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check the <guilabel>Do not track usage for this activity</guilabel> item to "
"switch off any tracking for your activity."
msgstr ""
"Označite element <guilabel>Ne spremljaj uporabe za to dejavnost</guilabel>, "
"da izklopite sledenje za svojo dejavnost."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shortcut for switching"
msgstr "Bližnjica za preklop"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press the first button to input the new shortcut to switch to the activity. "
"Press the second button to remove the current shortcut."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite prvi gumb, da vnesete novo bližnjico za preklop na dejavnost. Če "
"želite odstraniti trenutno bližnjico, pritisnite drugi gumb."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking on the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-"
"delete.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> button "
"removes the activity."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-delete."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> gumb odstranite "
"dejavnost."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking on the <guibutton>Create New...</guibutton> button below the list "
"opens <guilabel>Create a New Activity</guilabel> dialog which is similar to "
"the activity configuration dialog described above."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na gumb <guibutton>Ustvari novo...</guibutton> pod seznamom se "
"odpre pogovorno okno <guilabel>Ustvari novo dejavnost</guilabel>, ki je "
"podobno zgoraj opisanemu pogovornemu oknu za konfiguracijo dejavnosti."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switching"
msgstr "Preklapljanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here, you can configure if &plasma; should remember the <guilabel>Current "
"virtual desktop</guilabel> for each activity (needs restart). It is also "
"possible to configure shortcuts for walking through the list of activities."
msgstr ""
"Tu lahko nastavite, ali naj si &plasma; zapomni <guilabel>Prihodnje "
"virtualno namizje</guilabel> za vsako dejavnost (potrebuje ponovni zagon). "
"Mogoče je tudi konfigurirati bližnjice za premikanje po seznamu dejavnosti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information on how to use the &kde; shortcut system, see the <ulink "
"url=\"help:/fundamentals/shortcuts.html\"><emphasis>Using and Customizing "
"Shortcuts</emphasis> section of the <emphasis>&kde; Fundamentals</emphasis> "
"documentation</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij o uporabi sistema bližnjic &kde; glejte <ulink url=\"help:/"
"fundamentals/shortcuts.html\"><emphasis>Uporaba in prilagajanje bližnjic</"
"emphasis> v razdelku <emphasis>&kde; Fundamentals</emphasis> dokumentacije</"
"ulink>."

